284
00:15:43,109 --> 00:15:47,345
I just... I can't
believe this is my life.

285
00:15:50,366 --> 00:15:54,318
I don't understand. How did this
happen? How could this happen?

286
00:15:56,906 --> 00:15:59,673
Injuries like these
happen very quickly.

287
00:15:59,776 --> 00:16:02,626
She probably didn't
feel any pain at all.

288
00:16:03,496 --> 00:16:05,830
Mr. Shanley...

289
