According to Erin's driver's
license, she was an organ donor.

290
00:16:13,305 --> 00:16:15,372
And as next of kin,

291
00:16:15,474 --> 00:16:19,226
if you agree to take
her off of life-support,

292
00:16:19,328 --> 00:16:22,647
