heart to yourself.

293
00:16:25,952 --> 00:16:28,436
She is young, she was healthy.

294
00:16:28,538 --> 00:16:30,571
She would be a perfect
match for you, sir.

295
00:16:30,673 --> 00:16:32,423
Could you just please go away?

296
00:16:32,525 --> 00:16:36,910
- Mr. Shanley, if you would...
- Please. Please go away. Please.

297
00:16:38,748 --> 00:16:41,966
