298
00:16:42,068 --> 00:16:43,668
If you'd like.

299
00:16:52,979 --> 00:16:56,830
- Oh, so sorry. Excuse me. Are you OK?
- No. No apology necessary.

300
00:16:56,932 --> 00:16:59,784
I'm Sydney. Dr. Sydney
Heron. General surgery.

301
00:16:59,886 --> 00:17:01,169
Big fan of your work. Yeah.

302
00:17:01,271 --> 00:17:03,337
We were seated
together once at an M & M.

303
00:17:03,439 --> 00:17:04,671
Anyway.

304
00:17:04,773 --> 00:17:07,307
Now seems as good as
time as any to make it official.

305
00:17:07,426 --> 00:17:10,177
- Our introduction.
- Derek Shepherd. Pleasure.

306
00:17:10,280 --> 00:17:11,945
It's very, very
nice to meet you.

307
00:17:12,047 --> 00:17:14,632
Nice meeting you too.

308
00:17:18,654 --> 00:17:22,390
- You think she's pretty?
- Yeah. I like cheerful people.

309
00:17:22,492 --> 00:17:23,691
I can be cheerful.

310
00:17:23,793 --> 00:17:26,577
I think the ashes thing
makes that kind of unlikely.

311
00:17:28,147 --> 00:17:30,548
Dr. Bailey? We're going to help

312
00:17:30,649 --> 00:17:33,350
