ears today, pro bono,

313
00:17:33,453 --> 00:17:36,370
and I thought maybe you
could donate some time.

314
00:17:36,473 --> 00:17:38,506
Thanks to the fine
upstanding citizen

315
00:17:38,608 --> 00:17:40,374
