her off the roof.

339
00:19:15,872 --> 00:19:17,655
She was afraid of heights.

340
00:19:17,757 --> 00:19:21,908
They're ashes, Meredith.
The ashes aren't acrophobic.

341
00:19:22,010 --> 00:19:25,329
I need to put my mother to
rest. I need to not become her.

342
00:19:25,431 --> 00:19:27,965
I need to not die emotionally
crippled and alone.

343
00:19:28,067 --> 00:19:30,701
And I need to not
attend the wedding

344
00:19:30,803 --> 00:19:32,931
